Ext.data.JsonP['Alloy_1.8.1_Release_Note']({"guide":"<?xml version=\"1.0\" encoding=\"UTF-8\" ?>\n<!DOCTYPE html PUBLIC \"-//W3C//DTD XHTML 1.0 Transitional//EN\"\n        \"http://www.w3.org/TR/xhtml1/DTD/xhtml1-transitional.dtd\">\n<html xmlns=\"http://www.w3.org/1999/xhtml\">\n<head>\n    <title>Alloy 1.8.1 - 21 March 2016</title>\n\n    <meta http-equiv=\"Content-Type\" content=\"text/html; charset=UTF-8\">\n    <meta content=\"Scroll EclipseHelp Exporter\" name=\"generator\">\n\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\">\n    <link type=\"text/css\" rel=\"stylesheet\" media=\"print\">\n</link></link></link></meta></meta></head>\n<body>\n    <div class=\"container\">\n        <div class=\"header\"/>\n\n        <div id=\"src-46247139\" class=\"content\">\n                        <h1>Alloy 1.8.1 - 21 March 2016</h1>\n    <p>Alloy 1.8.1 is a patch release that includes one new feature, one improvement and one bug fix.    </p>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46247139_Alloy1.8.1ReleaseNote-NewFeature\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>New Feature</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1360\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1360</a> - Support for defining controller baseController in XML    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46247139_Alloy1.8.1ReleaseNote-Improvement\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Improvement</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1254\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1254</a> - Support model transform() in collection data-binding    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n    <div class=\"section section-2 \" id=\"src-46247139_Alloy1.8.1ReleaseNote-FixedIssue\">\n        <h2 class=\"heading \"><span>Fixed Issue</span></h2>\n<ul class=\" \"><li class=\" \">    <p><a class=\"external-link external-link\" href=\"https://jira.appcelerator.org/browse/ALOY-1369\" target=\"_blank\">ALOY-1369</a> - Complex data binding for collection doesn&apos;t work with transform    </p>\n</li></ul>    </div>\n        </div><a id=\"editButton\" href=\"https://wiki.appcelerator.org/pages/editpage.action?pageId=46247139\"><span>Edit</span></a>\n    \n        \n    </div>\n</body>\n</html>\n","title":"Alloy 1.8.1 Release Note"});